text: KLSX (99.1 FM) was a radio station licensed to Rozet, Wyoming, United States. The station was owned by Family Voice Communications, LLC. The station's owners surrendered its license to the Federal Communications Commission on June 5, 2018; the FCC cancelled the license the same day. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Campbell County, Wyoming LSX Category:Radio stations established in 2010 Category:2010 establishments in Wyoming Category:Radio stations disestablished in 2018 Category:2018 disestablishments in Wyoming Category:Defunct radio stations in the United States LSX
